<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2 style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; clear: both; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; font-weight: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 1.65em; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      Kerry-Lugar-Udall Visa Bill Will Create Jobs in America
    </h2>
    <font size="13px"><strong style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; text-transform: uppercase; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px" class="immediate-release">FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE</span>: Monday, March 14, 2011</strong></font><br />

    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">&#160;</span></font>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">WASHINGTON, D.C. &#8211; Senators John Kerry (D-Mass.) and Richard Lugar (R-Ind.), the Chairman and Ranking Member of the Senate Foreign Relations Committee, along with Senator Mark Udall (D-Colo.), today reintroduced legislation to drive job creation and increase America&#8217;s global competiveness by helping immigrant entrepreneurs secure visas to the United States.&#160;&#160;Congresswoman Carolyn</span><span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span><em style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">Maloney (D-N.Y.) plans to introduce companion legislation in the House.</span></em></font>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">The</span><span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span><em style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">StartUp Visa Act of 2011</span></em><span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">will allow an immigrant entrepreneur to receive a two year visa if he or she can show that a qualified U.S. investor is willing to invest in the immigrant&#8217;s startup venture.&#160;&#160;And in an expansion from the</span><span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span><em style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">Kerry-Lugar StartUp Visa Act of 2010</span></em><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">, the pool of eligible immigrants would now include holders of H-1B visas and entrepreneurs living outside the United States with a market presence in the country.</span></font>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">&#8220;Every job-creating American business started as an idea in the mind of an entrepreneur.&#160;&#160;We need to keep and bring more of those ideas to our shores where they can put Americans to work.&#160;&#160;Global competition for talent and investment grows more intense daily and the United States must step up or be left behind,&#8221; said Sen. Kerry.&#160;&#160;&#8220;Everywhere Dick Lugar and I travel for the Foreign Relations Committee, we see firsthand the entrepreneurial spirit driving the economies of our competitors.&#160; Creating a new magnet for innovations and innovators to come to the United States and create jobs here will offer our economy a double shot in the arm &#8211; robust job creation at home and reaffirmation that we&#8217;re the world&#8217;s best place to do business.&#8221;</span></font>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">&#8220;We want to establish a way for the smartest and most entrepreneurial individuals in the world to come to the United States and create jobs. Many are already here studying at our great universities,&#8221; said Sen. Lugar.&#160;&#160;&#8220;Helping them stay to invest in their ideas and create jobs benefits all Americans.&#8221;</span></font>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">&#8220;Our broken immigration system prevents talented entrepreneurs from all over the world from developing ideas that keep America competitive in a global economy.&#160;&#160;While I believe broader reform of the immigration system is long overdue, this fix is important to ensure we don&#8217;t unnecessarily hinder the innovators and entrepreneurs who will help drive America&#8217;s future economy,&#8221; said Sen. Udall.</span></font>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">&#8220;The entrepreneurial spirit among immigrants is ingrained in our country&#8217;s history and success,&#8221; said Rep. Maloney. &#8220;This legislation will promote our competitiveness around the globe and create a new generation of prosperity here at home by helping highly-skilled talent-- wherever in the world it comes from--to create companies and jobs in the U.S.&#8221;</span></font>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><strong style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px"><u>Options for Entrepreneurs</u></font></strong></span>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><strong style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px"><u>&#160;</u></font></strong></span><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small">The</font></span><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span></font><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><em style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px">StartUp Visa Act of 2011</font></em></span><span class="Apple-converted-space"><font size="small" face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif">&#160;</font></span><font size="small" face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">would amend immigration law to give immigrant entrepreneurs three new options for entry or retention of residency:</span></font>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><strong style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px">Option One:</font></strong></span><span class="Apple-converted-space"><font size="small" face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif">&#160;</font></span><font size="small" face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">Immigrant entrepreneurs living outside the U.S. would be eligible to apply for a StartUp Visa if a qualified U.S. investor agrees to financially sponsor their entrepreneurial venture with a minimum investment of $100,000. After two years, their business must have created 5 new jobs and raised not less than $500,000 in additional capital investment or generate not less than $500,000 in revenue.</span></font>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><strong style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px">Option Two:</font></strong></span><span class="Apple-converted-space"><font size="small" face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif">&#160;</font></span><font size="small" face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">Immigrant entrepreneurs currently in the U.S. on an unexpired H-1B visa;</span><span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span></font><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-decoration: underline; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px"><u>OR</u></font></span><span class="Apple-converted-space"><font size="small" face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif">&#160;</font></span><font size="small" face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">immigrant entrepreneurs currently in the U.S. who have completed a graduate level degree in science, technology, engineering, math, computer science, or other relevant academic discipline from an accredited United States college, university, or other institution of higher education would be eligible for a StartUp Visa if;</span></font>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small">They demonstrate annual income of not less than roughly $30,000 or the possession of assets of not less than roughly $60,000; and</font></span>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small">Have proven that a qualified U.S. investor agrees to financially back their entrepreneurial venture with a minimum investment of $20,000.</font></span>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small">After two years, their business must have created 3 new jobs and raised not less than $100,000 in additional capital investment or generate not less than $100,000 in revenue.</font></span>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><strong style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px">Option Three:</font></strong></span><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px"><span class="Apple-converted-space"><strong style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">&#160;</strong></span></font><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small">Immigrant entrepreneurs living outside the U.S. would be eligible to apply for a StartUp Visa if they have controlling interest of a company in a foreign country that has generated, during the most recent 12-month period, not less than $100,000 in revenue from sales in the U.S.&#160;</font></span>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small">After two years, their business must have created 3 new jobs and raised not less than $100,000 in additional capital investment or generate not less than $100,000 in revenue.</font></span>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><strong style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px"><u>Better Utilizing Existing Visas</u></font></strong></span>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small">To accommodate this new type of visa, adjustments would be made to the existing EB-5 visa &#8211; which grants visas to foreign nationals who invest $1 million towards the creation of 10 jobs. Under a new EB-6 category, a visa would be granted to the innovative entrepreneur with intellectual capital, instead of a wealthy foreign investor who is in a position to buy a visa. The legislation transfers an allotment of the yearly 9,940 EB-5 visas, of which only 4,191 visas were used in FY 2009, to be granted under the new EB-6 category.</font></span><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span></font><span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><strong style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px">The creation of new visas is not authorized in this bill.</font></strong></span>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><strong style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="13px"><u>Preventing fraud and abuse</u></font></strong></span>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small">The investor(s) eligible to &#8220;sponsor&#8221; immigrant entrepreneurs must be based in the U.S. - with the majority of partners being U.S. citizens - and have made $10 million capital commitments over the course of 2 years, with at least four investments exceeding $500,000 as stipulated in applicable SEC investor rules.</font></span>
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      
    </p>
    <p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right-width: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; text-align: center; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 13px; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px">
      <span style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: repeat; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-color: black; margin-top: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: small; background-image: initial; border-top-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-left-width: 0px"><font face="arial, helvetica, sans-serif" size="small"># # #</font></span>
    </p>
