    </p>
    <p style="padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; display: block; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.5em; margin-left: 8px; padding-left: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px">
      Lean startups aren't cheap startups: <a href="http://steveblank.com/2009/11/02/lean-startups-aren%E2%80%99t-cheap-startups/">http://steveblank.com/2009/11/02/lean-startups-aren%E2%80%99t-cheap-startups/</a>
    </p>
    <p style="padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; display: block; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.5em; margin-left: 8px; padding-left: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px">
      
    </p>
    <p style="padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; display: block; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.5em; margin-left: 8px; padding-left: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px">
      Lean startup wiki: <a href="http://leanstartup.pbworks.com/w/page/15765221/FrontPage">http://leanstartup.pbworks.com/w/page/15765221/FrontPage </a>
    </p>
    <p style="padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0; display: block; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.5em; margin-left: 8px; padding-left: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px">
