<node COLOR="#990000" CREATED="1311605050137" ID="ID_1023244979" MODIFIED="1313205883272" TEXT="Friends &amp; Family">
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(71, 71, 71)">Most often, money from friends and family is the first round of financing. </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(71, 71, 71)">There are some negative sides of having your family or friends invest in your company. A high percentage of startups fail, and there is a risk of losing both your friend&#8217;s money and the friendship itself. Family reunions can become more about what the startup is doing than it is about catching up with people you care about. </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(71, 71, 71)">It is recommended that you only take money from people that you know can afford to lose it. Be clear about the risk upfront.</font>&#160;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      [ <a href="http://mashable.com/2011/06/10/raise-funds-startup/">http://mashable.com/2011/06/10/raise-funds-startup/</a>&#160;]
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
