<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <span class="Apple-converted-space"><font size="12px" face="verdana, geneva, sans-serif" color="rgb(17, 17, 17)">&#160;M</font></span><font size="12px" face="verdana, geneva, sans-serif" color="rgb(17, 17, 17)"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: left; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-variant: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 15px" class="Apple-style-span">ost accelerators offer a stipend (~$15-25K is typical for 3-6 months) in exchange for equity in the startup (3-6% is common). </span></font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-transform: none; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: left; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-variant: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 15px" class="Apple-style-span"><font size="12px" face="verdana, geneva, sans-serif" color="rgb(17, 17, 17)">[</font></span>&#160;<a href="http://www.pittsburghventures.com/2011/01/accelerators-vs-incubators/">http://www.pittsburghventures.com/2011/01/accelerators-vs-incubators/</a>&#160;<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-transform: none; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: left; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-variant: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 15px" class="Apple-style-span"><font size="12px" face="verdana, geneva, sans-serif" color="rgb(17, 17, 17)">] </font></span>
    </p>
