<node COLOR="#111111" CREATED="1311607338322" ID="ID_545195302" LINK="http://www.techstars.org/" MODIFIED="1313205883315" TEXT="Techstars">
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <span style="background-color: rgb(245, 243, 233); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 17px" class="Apple-style-span"><font size="13px" face="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="rgb(51, 51, 51)">TechStars is a mentorship-driven seed stage investment program. We run a three month long program in Boston (MA), Boulder (CO), New York City (NY) and Seattle (WA) once each year. We&#8217;re very selective - hundreds of companies apply and we only take about ten companies per city. These companies get up to $18,000 in seed funding, three months of intensive</font></span><font size="13px" face="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="rgb(51, 51, 51)"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span></font><a href="http://www.techstars.org/mentors" style="padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; font-style: inherit; color: rgb(110, 145, 163); padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-decoration: underline"><font size="13px" face="inherit" color="rgb(110, 145, 163)"><span style="background-color: rgb(245, 243, 233); text-transform: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 17px" class="Apple-style-span"><u>top-notch mentorship</u></span></font></a><font size="13px" face="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="rgb(51, 51, 51)"><span style="background-color: rgb(245, 243, 233); text-transform: none; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-spacing: 0px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant: normal; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; line-height: 17px" class="Apple-style-span">, and the chance to pitch to angel investors and venture capitalists at the end of the program. </span></font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
