<node COLOR="#111111" CREATED="1311607885400" ID="ID_1266331002" LINK="http://founderfuel.com/en/" MODIFIED="1313205883320" TEXT="Founderfuel">
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <h3 style="padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: junctionregularRegular, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font-size: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-weight: normal; border-color: black; font-style: normal; border-right-width: 0px; color: rgb(26, 147, 212); font-variant: normal; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; line-height: 1.333em; vertical-align: baseline">
      FUNDING
    </h3>
    <p style="padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: SansSerif; margin-bottom: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font-size: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-weight: normal; border-color: black; font-style: normal; border-right-width: 0px; font-variant: normal; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline">
      Each team in the program receives a $10K investment, plus an additional $5K per co-founder in exchange for 6% equity in the company. As an example, a team of 3 will receive a total of $25K.
    </p>
    <p style="padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: SansSerif; margin-bottom: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font-size: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-weight: normal; border-color: black; font-style: normal; border-right-width: 0px; font-variant: normal; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline">
      &#160;
    </p>
    <p style="padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: SansSerif; margin-bottom: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font-size: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-weight: normal; border-color: black; font-style: normal; border-right-width: 0px; font-variant: normal; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline">
      This is ample money to get your company off the ground and ready for subsequent funding, which is exactly what we&#8217;re trying to help you accomplish.
    </p>
    <p style="padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: SansSerif; margin-bottom: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font-size: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-weight: normal; border-color: black; font-style: normal; border-right-width: 0px; font-variant: normal; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline">
      
    </p>
    <h3 style="padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: junctionregularRegular, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font-size: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-weight: normal; border-color: black; font-style: normal; border-right-width: 0px; color: rgb(26, 147, 212); font-variant: normal; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; line-height: 1.333em; vertical-align: baseline">
      TYPES OF STARTUPS
    </h3>
    <p style="padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: SansSerif; margin-bottom: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font-size: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-weight: normal; border-color: black; font-style: normal; border-right-width: 0px; font-variant: normal; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline">
      Web and mobile is what we&#8217;re all about, so you&#8217;re at the right place if that&#8217;s your thing.
    </p>
    <p style="padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: SansSerif; margin-bottom: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font-size: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-weight: normal; border-color: black; font-style: normal; border-right-width: 0px; font-variant: normal; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline">
      &#160;
    </p>
    <p style="padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: SansSerif; margin-bottom: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font-size: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-weight: normal; border-color: black; font-style: normal; border-right-width: 0px; font-variant: normal; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline">
      The program is intense and going through it alone is not something we recommend. Find a co-founder or two, and apply as a team. You&#8217;ll be more productive and get to your goals faster.
    </p>
    <p style="padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: SansSerif; margin-bottom: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font-size: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-weight: normal; border-color: black; font-style: normal; border-right-width: 0px; font-variant: normal; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline">
      
    </p>
    <p style="padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: SansSerif; margin-bottom: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font-size: inherit; margin-top: 0px; font-weight: normal; border-color: black; font-style: normal; border-right-width: 0px; font-variant: normal; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline">
      
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
