<node BACKGROUND_COLOR="#ffff00" COLOR="#0033ff" CREATED="1311293053681" ID="ID_1078229818" MODIFIED="1322582968336" POSITION="left" TEXT="Money $$">
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Startup finance is personal finance. When you can start your own business is going to be partially dependent on your personal financial situation&#8212;how stable your finances currently are.
    </p>
