<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      In 2000, the average cost to launch a technology startup was $1,000,000. Today, it&#8217;s about $50,000. And following the plan in this book, you&#8217;ll be able to start up for even less.
    </p>
    <p>
      [Edwards, Elizabeth (2010-12-15). Startup: The Complete Handbook for Launching a Company for Less (Kindle Locations 75-77). Essential Books. Kindle Edition. ]
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
